 ğŸ§ª Machine Learning Pipeline

1. ğŸ§¹ Data Cleaning & Exploration
   - Distribution plots, correlation matrix, pair plots
2. ğŸ“Š Feature Selection
   - Check for multicollinearity
   - Identify most influential features
3. ğŸ§  Model Building
   - Linear Regression
   - Train/Test split
4. ğŸ§® Evaluation Metrics
   - MAE, RMSE, RÂ² Score
5. ğŸ” Residual Analysis
   - To verify assumptions of linear regression



